data.description: Lovely Very Well Maintained Three Bedroom Two-Story out in the Country sits on .99 Acre. Nice size Living room. Large Kitchen with snack bar, Pantry closet. ALL APPLIANCES  STAY! 1/2 Bath and Spacious Rec-room with Woodburning Stove. Upper Level features Three Bedrooms with Hardwood floors and Ceiling fans. Full Bath. Main Bedroom has walk in closet. 2017 New Siding, Gutters, Soffits and Exterior Doors. New Garage Door 2016. New Concrete Patio 2022. New Windows PLUS 4 additional windows added to West side of home 2017. 2 Car Garage with Over Head Furnace. Hebron Address with Lowell Schools. LOW LOW TAXES! GREAT PLACE TO CALL HOME! :)
